Run: 



Reference:

[1] Aharon, Michal, Michael Elad, and Alfred Bruckstein. "K-SVD: An algorithm for designing overcomplete dictionaries for sparse representation." 
IEEE Transactions on signal processing 54.11 (2006): 4311-4322



